Introduction

Apink Y.O.S is a sub-unit of the South Korean girl group Apink, formed by members Bomi, Naeun, and Hayoung. The group was first introduced on April Fool's of 2018 and eventually debuted with a track for the television drama “School 2017.” On April 13, 2020, they released “Love is Blind,” a song included in Apink’s mini-album “LOOK.”
